    "slug": "plug-in-solar-for-rv-and-van-life",
    "title": "Plug-in Solar for RVs and Van Life: Go Off-Grid Affordably",
    "excerpt": "Portable solar panels for RVs, boondocking power strategies, and pairing with portable power stations.",
    "date": "2026-04-06",
